(firstQuint)Comparative Evaluation of Two Different Radiosurgery.

 This is a prospective double arm phase III study to evaluate cerebral side effects following radiosurgery delivered by Gamma Knife Perfexion and Linac Based EDGE.

 In particular our primary objective is to evaluate rate of symptomatic radionecrosis from the two different modalities of radiosurgery.

